originalText.text: Laura is an incredible psychic and healer. I’ve had a couple of readings with her and both were very good. The most recent one she did for me unlocked some new things for me, and it’s hard to explain, but I’ll say that it really has assisted me in getting to the next level of what I’ve been creating. I highly recommend Laura. She has an interesting reading style that she channels when she’s talks and sometimes it doesn’t make sense or sounds like gibberish but when you listen back to it a few days later it makes total and complete sense and it’s very insightful and she gives you action steps. Laura, I wish you all the blessings in the world and to whoever is reading this, book a session or two or three with Laura, her abilities are incredible. She’s can really help you move forward on your path
